dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: The Minerals data set shows the location of potential mining sites. Mineral resources are designated or prioritized in the General Policy Plan based on criteria related to land use, environmental and other relevant considerations, and conserved through policy and regulatory measures.Derivative data is routinely refreshed as the master data set is updated.
